title: [Feywrot Mire, Highland]
description: The ground is littered with a thick layer of crisp brown leaves that crunch underfoot.  Downslope to the west, pools of murky water lie stagnant on the ground.  A perpetual, misty fog hangs in the air, blocking even an occasional glimspe of the starry black skies.
